spital workflow, it allows you to increase patient volume without increasing staff. Integration of all application tasks reduces errors and increases productivity at all levels. With more accurate capture and reporting of patient data, diagnosed tests can be analysed to avoid duplications, reduce cycle times and maximize the throughput of the clinic or hospital. All this leads to improvement in the patient care.\r\n\t\t    </p>", "WEBSITE": "www.kodymedical.com", "CREATED_ON": "2019-01-28T12:15:05", "UPDATED_ON": "2019-04-10T14:50:07.836", "DATAMODE": "A"}}, {"model": "kodys.ma_application_manuals", "pk": 1, "fields": {"NAME": "Doppler Test Interpretation", "CATEGORY": "INTERPRETATION", "SUB_CATEGORY": "DOPPLER", "DESCRIPTION": "Doppler Test Interpretation File Path", "MANUAL_PATH": "/site_data/documents/Doppler_Interpretations.pdf", "CREATED_ON": "2019-01-28T12:15:05", "UPDATED_ON": "2019-01-28T12:15:05", "DATAMODE": "A"}}, {"model": "kodys.ma_application_manuals", "pk": 2, "fields": {"NAME": "Biothezi VPT Test Interpretation", "CATEGORY": "INTERPRETATION", "SUB_CATEGORY": "BIOTHEZIVPT", "DESCRIPTION": "Biothezi VPT Test Interpretation File Path", "MANUAL_PATH": "/site_data/documents/Biothezi_VPT.pdf", "CREATED_ON": "2019-01-28T12:15:06", "UPDATED_ON": "2019-01-28T12:15:06", "DATAMODE": "A"}}, {"model": "kodys.ma_application_manuals", "pk": 3, "fields": {"NAME": "Biothezi VPT Ultra Test Interpretation", "CATEGORY": "INTERPRETATION", "SUB_CATEGORY": "BIOTHEZIVPTULTRA", "DESCRIPTION": "Biothezi VPT Ultra Test Interpretation File Path", "MANUAL_PATH": "/site_data/documents/Biothezi_VPT_Ultra.pdf", "CREATED_ON": "2019-01-28T12:15:07", "UPDATED_ON": "2019-01-28T12:15:07", "DATAMODE": "A"}}, {"model": "kodys.ma_application_manuals", "pk": 4, "fields": {"NAME": "Kodys HCP - Elite Test Interpretation", "CATEGORY": "INTERPRETATION", "SUB_CATEGORY": "KODYSHCPELITE", "DESCRIPTION": "Kodys HCP Elite Test Interpretation File Path", "MANUAL_PATH": "/site_data/documents/HCP_Eleit